{"TopicId":167317,"ForumId":39,"TopicTitle":"My mother passed away ... so I made her a star","CreatedByName":"Azimech","CreatedById":50750,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-07T22:05:40Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Azimech","CreatedById":50750,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-07T22:05:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEveryone grieves in his/her own way. KSP is currently my only way of expressing myself creatively.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s a simple rocket, no need to steer, just tap stage a few times.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd it launches at dawn.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022WQ3dLXP.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022768\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/WQ3dLXP.png\u0022 width=\u0022960\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEnd of the first stage. The fairing is released as well\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Ni8yQEb.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022768\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/Ni8yQEb.png\u0022 width=\u0022960\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEnough delta-v.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022KuYjPee.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022768\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/KuYjPee.png\u0022 width=\u0022960\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe last separation.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022BrhshrF.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022768\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/BrhshrF.png\u0022 width=\u0022960\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022evILklJ.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022768\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/evILklJ.png\u0022 width=\u0022960\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-07T22:22:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot sure what to say.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m sorry for your loss.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTime heals all wounds my friend.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"katateochi","CreatedById":35181,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-07T23:06:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAzimech, amigo, I\u0027m so sorry for you man. Give me a yell if you want to chat.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DarkOwl57","CreatedById":161624,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-07T23:57:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m so sorry, man. So sorry..\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-08T00:15:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou have my condolences.\u00A0 So sorry for your loss.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNever forget her, she will always live in you heart and memory\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"/not/pol/","CreatedById":172548,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-08T01:00:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry for your loss man..\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DunnoAnyThing","CreatedById":180004,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-08T06:50:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nShocked to hear this news..\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo sorry for your loss.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Castille7","CreatedById":101668,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-09T22:46:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVery sorry to hear this Azimech, sorry for the loss man\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset 