Name":"Kevin Kyle","CreatedById":110492,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-09T23:04:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy heart goes out to you\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpaceN00b","CreatedById":179916,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-09T23:05:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am so sorry \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/50750-azimech/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002250750\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/50750-azimech/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Azimech\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NSEP","CreatedById":165635,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-10T11:11:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry for your loss,\u00A0Azimech. Amazing\u00A0start you made for her, by the way.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbalwerks","CreatedById":175668,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-10T22:12:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ernos","CreatedById":97086,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-11T07:50:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry for your loss, Azimech. Amazing star.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-11T08:13:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy condolences, Mate.\u00A0 But what a beautiful tribute.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MinimalMinmus","CreatedById":172387,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-12T22:56:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am sorry for your loss. May this new star shine forever.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FleshJeb","CreatedById":111640,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-14T00:19:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m sorry Azi. That\u0027s a stunning tribute, and it says everything.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RoadRunnerAerospace","CreatedById":177973,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-14T03:26:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry for your loss, but a excellent tribute\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"gamingknight","CreatedById":175269,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-17T21:20:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsorry for your loss i\u0027m touched that you made a star in her honor in you (possibly) favorite game\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nand i hope you overcome this headle\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbinchaser","CreatedById":160817,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-17T21:31:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nReally sorry for your loss Azi. I understand losing people. It\u0027s sad, but what a wonderful and touching tribute for your Mother.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGreat job.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dud3x","CreatedById":182303,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-19T21:19:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m really sorry for that your mother passed away. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope things will get better soon \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AHeroReborn","CreatedById":173981,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-19T21:44:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nY\u0027know, some people say video games are stupid, and they can\u0027t understand that stupid is relative. Don\u0027t let anyone tell you that launching a virtual\u00A0ship for your mom is dumb. It\u0027s no more dumb then burying them in a wooden box or burning them to ashes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlthough I\u00A0have to ask. are those lots of lights? if so, how are they powered?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Azimech","CreatedById":50750,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-19T22:25:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223223359\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022167317\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221511127877\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022173981\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AHeroReborn\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n29 minutes ago, AHeroReborn said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nY\u0027know, some people say video games are stupid, and they can\u0027t understand that stupid is relative. Don\u0027t let anyone tell you that launching a virtual\u00A0ship for your mom is dumb. It\u0027s no more dumb then burying them in a wooden box or burning them to ashes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlthough I\u00A0have to ask. are those lots of lights? if so, how are they powered?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe construction of the star is as follows: I took a short girder and mounted radially a whole bunch of flat radiators (radiators are the best at reflecting light). Then, I autostrutted the radiators. I mounted a whole bunch of MK2 spotlights, also radially, front and aft of the radiators, shining at the right angle. Then I copied the girder and mounted it at a 45 degree angle (to the right) and autostrutted to grandparent part. Then used offset to slide it into the center of the original girder. I repeated this two more times (90 degrees and 135 degrees from the base girder). Then I did it again but mounted at a 45 degree angle upwards and again two more times. Added a probe core and a few \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Radio-isotope Thermo-electric Generator (a.k.a. Mars rover heating device)\u0022\u003ERTG\u003C/abbr\u003E\u0027s and the star was ready.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"EpicSpaceTroll139","CreatedById":162839,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-19T22:42:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m sorry for your loss. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat a pretty remembrance item for your mom.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:rep:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/rep.png\u0022 title=\u0022:rep:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMay the little star live\u00A0on like her spirit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}